3. Mission & Objectives

Mission

To advance regulated, resilient, and trustworthy autonomous intelligence through international collaboration, open research, and shared governance.

Core Objectives
	1.	Develop and validate the QUENNE foundational architecture
	2.	Establish global benchmarks for resilience, energy efficiency, and stability
	3.	Coordinate cross-border pilot research programs
	4.	Promote open science and reproducibility
	5.	Serve as an advisory body for safe AI deployment

